    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've been reading online that garlic actually acts as a natural blood thinner and some people use it to avoid all these meds. if i just slowly tapered off the warfarin and replaced it with the garlic supplements and maybe some vitamin k adjustments, wouldn't that be a more holistic way to do it? it feels like way too much chemicals in the pills.",
